thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Robert Kyte

author: Robert Kyte
title: Robert Kyte
text: I, along with another co-executor, was tasked with the sale of 19 May Street Aberfeldie on behalf of a friend's estate. Nelson Alexander's Essendon branch was chosen to conduct the sale after due research and meetings with agents. Matt Febey was communicative, easy to deal with and knew his market. He is a specialist in the local area, and also has access to a wider reach through the firm's branch network across the north and west. Matt was ably assisted by Mark Turner. Matt's preparation and auctioneering skills are both strong, and a very good result was recorded on the day for my friend's family. Thanks for your efforts guys!
